In this candid interview, Sean recounts his painful past as a member of the Ramp School of Ministry and Chosen dance team. He shares how he was groomed and sexually abused by someone on staff - and how a pastor he confided in ignored his plea for help. 
Recorded on Tiktok Live on 3/15/25

